headline: BofA upgrades Public Storage, Extra Space as it sees storage REITS defensive
summary: Investing.com -- Bank of America upgraded Public Storage (NYSE:PSA) to Buy from Neutral and Extra Space Storage (NYSE:EXR) to Neutral from Underperform, citing a more positive outlook for the self storage sector relative to other REITs.
